reviewText: I love Hummingbirds!  I'm a birder.  I still use VHS tapes.  This VHS tape is beautiful.  It shows the beauty of the hummingbirds, how they can fly to the flowers and all around bringing about beauty with their color.  It proves that not all birds create sound but sound is not the only thing that brings out the beauty in a bird!
Bought this several years ago as gift for family member.  Have watched it many times.  Photography and music excellent as is narration.
